COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 9:14PM PT today, over 1.2 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 16.9 thousand have died.

In the last day, 2 thousand new infections were reported and 8 deaths. Currently 2,049 are in the hospital and 49 are in the ICU. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 22.1 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 5 years and older, 27.9% have their 1st shot and 19.7% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is slowing down, but there are 1 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~158 days for new deliveries to get into arms.

At the current rate, Canadians should achieve herd immunity around when 80% of the entire population is fully vaccinated. There is no approved vaccine for children under 5.

    76 in 100 are fully vaccinated.
